{"tid":187342,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[過唔過到關]長毛申領回鄉證考察東江水","createTime":"2017-04-05T01:04:47.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-05T05:11:02.000Z","uid":77196,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"51f1418791d9f490678df2e35d6dbc7fbc909685","tid":187342,"uid":77196,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-05T01:04:47.000Z","msg":"新一屆立法會本月中將首次組團到內地考察，下周五到廣東省考察東江水，為期兩天，目前已有20名議員報名，包括8名民主派議員。<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>唯一未持有回鄉證的社民連梁國雄亦有報名，他今天將申領回鄉證</strong></span>。<br />\n<br />\n已報名參與今次發展事務委員會內地考察團的民主派議員來自不同黨派，除梁國雄外還包括民主黨黃碧雲、公民黨陳淑莊、工黨張超雄、專業議政莫乃光、梁繼昌與邵家臻。梁國雄表示，相信今次不會有機會與中央官員會面。"},{"pid":"25d27f995402ec94d757828de0e8c05c076e135c","tid":187342,"uid":82929,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-05T02:09:04.000Z","msg":"返支那7<br />\n<br />\n反共唔反中<br />\n注定出賣香港人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6f0d5405a4cb0be3464aac79732891b09373a9dd","tid":187342,"uid":71257,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-05T02:42:14.000Z","msg":"肯定又著件平反64 t<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 之後比人拒入境<br />\n<br />\n再返香港開記者會<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2d73061ffeb38d806bf53109a1c3412a1e9ff1eb","tid":187342,"uid":802,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-05T02:54:29.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>肯定又著件平反64 t<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 之後比人拒入境<br />\n<br />\n再返香港開記者會<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"025f5547bb88c0acc7a6932ee6eea165f63bb207","tid":187342,"uid":77196,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-0